column5: Did quick 3 hours this afternoon and got 5 for 7. 3 Kings and 2 Bows. 330 fow seemed to work best. Michael Jackson and Black/Green NK28 spoons did all the damage. 30 feet down was the best depth. 5 to 13 Lbs. Not a bad day with the whole family on board. Here is a late/dark/not so good picture of few fish I dropped at friend's house.    Cheers, Ice Fisherman
Nice fish! Looks like you had a good time!
